value: Breeds tliroughout Europe and Asia, south of the tundra, south to north- ern Spain, northern Italy, southern Russia, Persia, Baluchistan, Kashmir, Mongolia, Manchuria and Japan. Winters in Madeira and on the Cape Verde Islands, all of Africa, India, Ceylon, southeastern Asia north to southern China and Formosa, the Philippines and the Malay Archi- pelago to Australia.
